            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(27, 95, 51); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Success!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Messages were sent to all test contacts in the loop.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;How it worked:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Each loop iteration ran in a &lt;b&gt;new transaction&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The SendMessage action made its callout&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Any DML was committed before the next iteration&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No &quot;uncommitted work pending&quot; errors occurred!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Remember:&lt;/b&gt; The key is setting &lt;code&gt;flowTransactionModel=NewTransaction&lt;/code&gt; in the flow metadata.&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
